.Dd April 29, 2000
.Dt CMPCI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm cmpci
.Nd C-Media CMI8x38 audio device driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "cmpci* at pci? dev ? function ?"
.Cd "audio* at cmpci?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
device driver supports C-Media CMI8x38 based sound cards.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr audio 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver appeared in
.Nx 1.5 .
.Sh BUGS
MPU-401 compatible MIDI port, OPL3 FM synthesizer, and joystick port are
not supported.  SPDIF in/out ports are not yet available.
